{"tid":1459776,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【你的名字】【圖文】（發夢）當和理非跟女烈士交換了身體","createTime":"2019-08-12T20:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:28:01.000Z","uid":265581,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"981d85375bb29f026602164eea6f4e56b8665bdc","tid":1459776,"uid":265581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:26:14.000Z","msg":"2019年，香城<br />\n我做了一個難以忘懷的夢，夢裡我遇上了一場將會毀了這個都市的災難、一群不得已衝破了法律枷鎖的少年。<br />\n<br />\n（一）<br />\n「我漸漸明白究竟發生了什麼事。龔三葉，和我同歲，是住在元朗的女高中生。」<br />\n「不定期會跟住在在港島的男高中生何理非交換身體，每周兩到三次，總是在睡着時交換，原因不明。」<br />\n「交換身體後的記憶在醒來後會變得越來越模糊。」<br />\n「但是我們確實交換了身體，為了不破壞彼此的生活，定下了規矩。」<br />\n「還有，交換後做的事情都要寫在日記上。為了解決這個謎之現象，我們兩個要互相協助。」<br />\n<br />\n「你不要.....」「注意......啊喂！」<br />\n（那個男的實在是！）（那個女的的實在是！）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAUhak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAUhak.png&h=ddf6a9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（二）<br />\n「其實&hellip;你正在做夢。」我驀地驚醒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3v7CZpA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3v7CZpA.png&h=713cc9b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbPBvwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbPBvwK.png&h=ad77cdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sRXeZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sRXeZy.png&h=5b0d61ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「不對，」<br />\n「那並不是夢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCEBvMV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYCEBvMV.png&h=c01efe7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「但三葉...在那以後就消失了」我找遍了這幾年香港的報紙在元朗的報導。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/949Bvyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F949Bvyd.png&h=1e310220&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「只是因為撐起了雨傘&hellip;嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLBL8ko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLBL8ko.png&h=fd2d0cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZQ5oT6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZQ5oT6.png&h=bdb7dc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「沒問題的，一定還來得及的，只要回到三葉消失的地方就...」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fVhe2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fVhe2b.png&h=d4b85f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSoyxQk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSoyxQk.png&h=5aae8169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（三）<br />\n「是三葉...她還生存...」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmd6SSY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkmd6SSY.png&h=1a07cc1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「在這樣下去，大家就死定了!」<br />\n「我們沒有加入他們，警察怎麼會打我們！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2y9qo8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2y9qo8v.png&h=36ec6e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這是我的雙眼看見的。」勅使盯着三葉的眼睛，「這就夠了！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「為了三葉和她珍視的一切，我們願意冒著成為罪人的風險，付上我們所能付出的任何代價！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKp9QGS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKp9QGS.png&h=26d4c495&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8397fe30c365e36a54ac525e3533d7a67e385f3a","tid":1459776,"uid":305822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:28:01.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}